Package server.ai.pathfinding

Class Node

java.lang.Object
server.ai.pathfinding.Node
public class Node
extends java.lang.Object
A node representing a grid square. Each node has a reference to a parent node as well as a coordinate location and f g values for heuristic pathfinding.
Author:
Daniel Batchford
